.profile
  .row
    .col-xs-12.col-md-1
      =image_tag("group-choice-2.png", style: "width:75px;")

    .col-xs-12.col-md-3
      %h1
        %b= @group.first.name
      %b Your Pillar Badges:
      .row
        .badges-progress
          -@levels.each do |l|
            .col-xs-1
              =div_for @user, class: (l.pillar > @user.level ? 'grey-badge' : 'color') do
                =image_tag(l.avatar.url, style: "width:25px;")
    .col-xs-12.col-md-6.col-md-offset-2
      .rule-box.text-center
        %h4 What Should I Do?
        %p 
          Pick your favorite challenges from the available list and complete them to receive 'Awesome Points' which go towards conquering the 
          ="#{level.name} pillar." 
          Once you collect 
          ="#{level.points}" 
          you earn your pillar badge.